research_municipality_step.notes: Information on elected officials for Florence city, TX, was primarily sourced from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory and the Texas State Directory Online, which are intended to list current officials. There was conflicting information regarding the Mayor and Mayor Pro-Tem in a City Council Agenda from March 2024, which listed Mary Condon as Mayor and Debra Bartos Cahill as Mayor Pro Tem, along with an additional Council Member, Amy Hannson. However, the directories were prioritized as they are official listings of current elected officials. The roles 'Alderwoman' and 'Alderman' were standardized to 'Council Member' for consistency.
